            <title>[LU-14725] zpool get stuck after sanity/27Q</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14725</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity/27Q creates a symbolik link from /tmp/xxx to a file on Lustre, then on a local setup (everything on a single node) another test (e.g. sanity/60a) stops MGS (so MDS) and tries to start MGS/MDS later, but zpool import scans /tmp, finds that symlink to a file on Lustre and gets stuck stat&apos;ing that file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
